  "comment": "Strike Array 2 is an outdoor-ready audience blinder powered by two intense 100 W warm white LEDs housed in independently focusable pods. An emulated \"amber shift\" warms the color temperature of the light as it dims to deliver a classic tungsten look. Its variable PWM and high CRI make it ideal for broadcast applications. Thanks to a custom interlocking system CHAUVET Professional has developed, STRIKE Array 2 can be interconnected with multiple Array units for scalable design configurations without any tools. Omega-Bracket locks are also installed both on the yoke and the back of the IP65 blinder to give you a streamlined truss mounting process.",
